---
title: Chermoula Spiced Paneer & Veggie Couscous with Lemony Yoghurt & Currants
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful paneer meets roasted vegetables tossed with chermoula spices, and there’s a tangy yoghurt dressing plus a smattering of juicy currants in the couscous to finish it off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-chermoula-paneer-roast-veggie-couscous-39b711fe.jpg
